node.text:
Music is the international language

🎼@thekiffness with 🐾  @thelifeofleocat

Production - The Kiffness (South Africa) 🇿🇦⠀
Vocals - @thelifeofleocat / NumNum Cat (Turkey) 🇹🇷⠀
Violin - @amanda_barbalho (Brazil) ⠀
Accordion - @lilmisssqueezbox (Australia)⠀
Vibe - Vibing Cat (Canada) 🇨🇦⠀
Trumpet - @samtmusic (Australia) 🇦🇺⠀
Djembe (African Drum) - Benjamin rocks! (Germany) 🇩🇪⠀

Numnum Cat now available for pre-save on Spotify and/or download on Bandcamp 😺🥛
bit.ly/numnumcat

#meowed #thekiffness #thelifeofleocat #soundon #volumup #🔊 #music #numnumcat #catconcert
